name: RYAN 13
description: "If wishes were horses, beggars would ride."  Ryan's no beggar, but his horse is something straight out of a pencil and watercolor dream, more wish and whim than blood and bone... if there's anything real here, it's his sabich sandwich, a pita stuffed with fried eggplant, soft boiled egg, and cucumber slices.  Ride with Ryan, sandwich stonks!
